item.description:
Upload all 5 sample TOSCA files to OptimusDB.

**Note:** You need to convert YAML files to base64 and set them as environment variables:
- {{webapp_adt_base64}}
- {{capacity_profile_base64}}
- {{opentofu_hybrid_base64}}
- {{deployment_plan_base64}}
- {{app_requirements_base64}}

Or use the Pre-request Script in each request to read files.

